<plot>The powers of the subconscious are explored in this curious film, which questions the fictionality of the dreaming mind. Evie awakens from a very peculiar, yet detailed dream, and struggles to remember it after experiencing an intense deja vu with a person she's never actually met before. When characters from her dream being to appear in her waking life, it begins to seem as if dreams are really portals, which allow one to temporarily experience an alternate universe.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?429691</url></doc>
